description: Another resident dies and two more positive cases connected to Abbotswood Nursing Home are confirmed.
title: Coronavirus: Abbotswood Nursing Home death toll rises to 19
title_page: Coronavirus: Abbotswood Nursing Home death toll rises to 19 - BBC News
maintext: There have been 316 cases of the virus on the Isle of Man and 271 are now "presumed recovered" after completing the mandatory 14-day isolation period.
